@startuml error-recovery-sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #3B82F6
  ArrowFontColor #64748B
  LifeLineBorderColor #3B82F6
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E0F2FE
  ParticipantBorderColor #3B82F6
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E0F2FE
  ParticipantFontColor #1E293B
  GroupBorderColor #F43F5E
  GroupFontColor #F43F5E
  DividerBorderColor #94A3B8
  DividerFontColor #64748B
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF3C7
  BorderColor #F59E0B
  FontColor #1E293B
}

title LingoBridge 弱网错误恢复时序图

participant "学生浏览器\n(Student Browser)" as browser
participant "前端 SPA\n(React)" as spa
participant "Vercel Proxy" as vercel
participant "后端 API\n(Express)" as backend

== 初始连接失败 ==

browser -> spa : 触发网络请求\n(如: Presence 心跳)
activate spa #E0F2FE

spa -> vercel : HTTPS 请求
activate vercel #F0FDF4
vercel ->x backend : 连接超时 / 网络不可达
vercel --> spa : **ERR_CONNECTION_TIMED_OUT**
deactivate vercel

spa -> spa : 检测到网络错误\n启动重试机制

note right of spa
  **指数退避策略:**
  T_wait = min(1000 × 2^n, 30000) ms
  n = 重试次数 (0..9)
  最大重试: 10 次
  抖动: ±20% 随机偏移
end note

== 指数退避重试过程 ==

loop 重试 n = 0..9 (最多 10 次)

  spa -> spa : 等待 T_wait ms\nT_wait = 1s → 2s → 4s → 8s → ...

  spa -> browser : 显示重连提示\n"正在重新连接... (第 n+1 次)"

  spa -> vercel : 重试请求
  activate vercel #F0FDF4

  alt 网络恢复 (成功路径)

    vercel -> backend : 转发请求
    activate backend #D1FAE5
    backend --> vercel : 200 OK
    deactivate backend
    vercel --> spa : 成功响应
    deactivate vercel

    == 成功路径: 重连与恢复 ==

    spa -> spa : 重置重试计数器 n = 0
    spa -> backend : 恢复 Presence 连接\n重新同步在线状态
    activate backend #D1FAE5
    backend --> spa : Presence 状态同步完成\n返回当前会话快照
    deactivate backend

    spa -> browser : 隐藏重连提示\n显示 "已恢复连接" ✓
    deactivate spa

  else 仍然失败 (继续重试)

    vercel -->x spa : 连接失败
    deactivate vercel
    spa -> spa : n++ 继续下一轮

  end

end

== 失败路径: 超过最大重试次数 ==

spa -> spa : n > 9\n重试耗尽

spa -> spa : **清理 MediaStream 资源**\nstream.getTracks().forEach(\n  t => t.stop()\n)

note right of spa #FEE2E2
  **媒体轨道清理:**
  1. 停止所有音频轨道 (mic)
  2. 停止所有视频轨道 (camera)
  3. 释放 MediaStream 引用
  4. 更新本地连麦状态为 "断开"
end note

spa -> browser : 显示超时警告弹窗\n"网络连接失败，请检查网络后重试"

browser -> spa : 用户点击 "返回首页"
spa -> browser : 导航至首页\nrouter.push('/')

deactivate spa

@enduml
